Steps for running load balancing:

0.  lbclient.pl must be running on all machines that will accept jobs. To start 
them, run launch_client.pl.  The arguments are the machines file for all the 
machines (this will be used by the clients to look up load levels as well), 
name of the lbclient.pl file (full path), and the load balancing directory.

1. Start lbserver.  Follow the information given on the command line to do this.

2. Submit jobs using load_balance.pl
